<h1>About NEXUS</h1>

<p>
    NEXUS is a collaboration platform where users can share early-stage project ideas,
    discover open projects, apply to contribute, and form teams after approval.
</p>

<p>
    In this MVP version, there is no real-time chat. The main workflow is:
    application, founder approval, and team visibility.
</p>